strings: <se_low>Kalderasha: Ah, you have returned?
<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. I sense you have not come to me for a social visit.
<se_low>Kalderasha: No doubt you have come to have your fortune told? Very well...
<se_low>Kalderasha: As it is you, I will make an exception and not ask for my palm to be crossed with gold coins.
<se_low>Kalderasha: You do not need to tell me what you want to know. My crystal ball will tell me everything.
<se_low>Kalderasha: What will it show today...? Hmmm...

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
I see the plains stretching away in the southwest of our continent.

<se_low>Kalderasha: And I see a mountain in the middle of them.
...No, wait! Is it a ship?
This is what you are searching for.

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. That is all I can tell you.
The rest you must figure out for yourself.
<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us that the thing you seek stands on the plains in the south-western corner of our continent.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
I see...a castle!

<se_low>Kalderasha: I see a castle...and a young king.
He is smiling happily.
The thing you seek is with him.

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. That is all I can tell you.
The rest you must figure out for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us that the thing you
seek is to be found at the castle of a happy,
young king.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
I see the continent to the west, far across
the sea, and a town with a big casino.

<se_low>Kalderasha: But there is something strange.
There is a casino, but it is so quiet...
What is going on?

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. That is all I can tell you.
The rest you must figure out for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us that you should
go to the distant western continent,
to a big casino town...

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
I see a place on the western continent...
A big town and a splendid castle.
<se_low>Kalderasha: It seems that the thing you seek is to be found there at the castle.

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. That is all I can tell you.
The rest you must figure out for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us that the thing you
seek is to be found in a big castle on the
western continent.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
This is the western continent...
I see a town built on top of a large bridge.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Hm? What is this...!?
I see the girl who is normally with you.
But she looks somehow different...

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm.
So it is the girl, Jessica, you are searching for.

<se_low>Kalderasha: I do not know how you have been separated,
but you must go to her at once.
<se_low>Kalderasha: It seems Jessica is in a town built on top of a large bridge.

<se_low>Kalderasha: I do not know why you were separated,
but you must go to her at once.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
I see a tower soaring into the sky in the south of our continent.
<se_low>Kalderasha: At the top of this tower is something glowing bright and strong. This is what you seek.

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. That is all I can tell you.
The rest you must figure out for yourself.
<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us that the thing you seek is to be found in an old tower in the south of this continent.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.
<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing!

<se_low>Kalderasha: Is this a ship...?
Yes! And an ancient ship too!
<se_low>Kalderasha: I see the ship sailing along a river... And then...
<se_low>Kalderasha: Ah! I think it is going into a cave!

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...That is all I can see.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.
<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us that the thing you seek is in a riverside cave that you can enter by ship.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
I see the southern continent...
And a place to the north of the labyrinth
with the statues holding swords.

<se_low>Kalderasha: And I see...a cascade of water nearby.
But it is a high place. Birds fly in and out
with ease. On foot, it would be impossible.

<se_low>Kalderasha: It seems that the thing you seek is to be
found there.
<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us the thing you seek is to be found in a high place where water cascades from the cliffs, somewhere north of the Swordsman's Labyrinth.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
It is flying through the sky...
A big black dog...
<se_low>Kalderasha: But you need some kind of guidance to find it.

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. It seems the guidance you need is
already in your possession.
You must use it and pursue this flying dog.

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. That is all I can tell you.
The rest you must figure out for yourself.
<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us that you must use something already in your possession to locate the flying black dog.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Yes! Yeeesss! The mists are clearing.
I see a sinister man making a speech at the foot of an enormous statue of the Goddess.
<se_low>Kalderasha: But he is surrounded by bodyguards and many followers. He will be hard to approach.

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...Hmm. That is all I can tell you.
The rest you must figure out for yourself.
<se_low>Kalderasha: The crystal ball told us that you should go to find the sinister man who is giving a speech at the foot of a giant Goddess statue.

<se_low>Kalderasha: Whether it is true or not, I do not know.
It is simply what I saw.
You must figure out the rest for yourself.

<se_low>Kalderasha: ...So, you know about the Monster Arena, hm?
Remember, the Great Kalderasha sees all!
You cannot hide things from my eyes.
<se_low>Kalderasha: Sometimes it may be...advantageous to empty your mind of your quest, and take part in this ‘sport’.
<se_low>Kalderasha: Do well in the arena, and you will find people are drawn to your success. One man could be so drawn, he may even wish to join your...wagon quest, perhaps?
